==English==
===Noun===
'''fastball''' (plural: fastballs)

#{{baseball}} A backspin [[pitch]] thrown with roughly equal pressure by the index and middle fingers, a [[four-seam fastball]]
#: ''The pitcher had a blazing '''fastball'''.''

